## Technical Implementation

### Build System
```bash
# Single command builds all binaries with synchronized versions
./build-with-version.sh v1.6.0

# Output:
# ✓ Main binary: portunix v1.6.0
# ✓ Helper binary: ptx-container v1.6.0
# ✓ Helper binary: ptx-mcp v1.6.0
```

### Installation
```bash
# Installs all binaries to target directory
./portunix install-self --silent --path /usr/local/bin/portunix

# Result:
# ✓ portunix installed
# ✓ ptx-container installed
# ✓ ptx-mcp installed
```

### Update Process
```bash
# Downloads archive, extracts all binaries, updates atomically
./portunix update

# Process:
# ✓ Download portunix_1.6.0_linux_amd64.tar.gz
# ✓ Verify checksums
# ✓ Extract all binaries
# ✓ Backup existing binaries
# ✓ Update all binaries atomically
```

