## Architecture Validation

### Directory Structure
```
/usr/local/bin/           # Installation directory
├── portunix              # Main dispatcher (23MB)
├── ptx-container         # Container helper (5.7MB)
└── ptx-mcp              # MCP helper (5.7MB)
```

### Command Flow
```
User Command: portunix container run ubuntu
      ↓
Main Dispatcher: portunix
      ↓ (delegates)
Helper Binary: ptx-container
      ↓ (executes)
Container Runtime: Docker/Podman
```

